# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Bot Worker — local: copy to `.dev.vars` in repo root (gitignored). Production:
# use Dashboard → Workers → hns-bot → Settings → Variables, or `wrangler secret put`.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# --- Secrets (wrangler secret put NAME — never commit real values) ------------
# DISCORD_TOKEN              Bot token (Discord → Bot → Reset Token)
# SESSION_SECRET             Same string as auth Worker; 32+ random bytes as hex or long passphrase
# GITHUB_OAUTH_CLIENT_SECRET If you use /link-github (GitHub OAuth app)
# GITHUB_LINK_SECRET         Random string; encrypts GitHub tokens in D1
# CLAUDE_API_KEY             Optional; monthly AI challenges (Anthropic)
#
# --- Also in wrangler.toml [vars] (or Dashboard → Variables → plain text) -------
# BASE_URL                   https://h4cknstack.com  (no trailing slash; must match site)
# DISCORD_GUILD_ID           Server ID (Discord → Server → right-click → Copy ID, dev mode on)
# DISCORD_PUBLIC_KEY         Developer Portal → General → Public Key
# DISCORD_APPLICATION_ID     Developer Portal → General → Application ID
# ADMIN_CHANNEL_ID, VOTING_CHANNEL_ID, BLOG_CHANNEL_ID, DEVELOPER_*, HACKER_*, ADMIN_ROLE_ID
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Slash command registration (local only) — `npm run register` from repo root
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# DISCORD_APPLICATION_ID     Same as above
# DISCORD_TOKEN              Same bot token
# DISCORD_TEST_GUILD_ID      Target guild for instant command updates (your server ID)

